# 🌿 Endangered Animals Evaluation

- 🚧 En progreso

![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0-67C090)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-Apache_2.0-AAFFC7)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-215B63)

## 📌 Description
---
A Streamlit-based interactive dashboard that uses Artificial Intelligence to classify endangered animal species and visualize global biodiversity data.

## 🚀 Features
---
- 🧠 AI image classification model
- 🌍 Interactive world map of endangered species
- 📊 Data visualization dashboards
- 🎯 Filtering by species type
- 📈 Prediction confidence analytics

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
---
- Python
- Streamlit
- TensorFlow / Keras
- Pandas
- PyDeck

